            "content_html": "\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Celebrity homes have always been in the media, doing rounds on the Internet and being talked about in full grace. Over the years, the trend depicts actors preferring Porsche and spacious residences for themselves. The fact that home is the place they spend most of the time apart from studios makes it worthwhile. Most Indian actors have proven to be spendthrifts when it comes to planning their abode. Similarly, the celeb home we are going to talk about here is the one owned by the famous south-Indian actor Allu Arjun.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Allu Arjun&#8217;s house in Hyderabad is an expansive one and includes unmissable amenities. Well, this blog intends to take our readers on a journey to witness each aspect of the very famous celebrity home. From child-friendly corners to party corners, the house has it all. It is expansive in the sense that hardly is there any area where one would feel closely packed.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-allu-arjun-s-journey\">Allu Arjun\u2019s Journey</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The south-Indian industry takes pride in beholding such great talents of all times. Allu Arjun has left no stone unturned in winning the hearts of fans. In the Telugu film industry, some of his famous hits include Naa Peru Surya, Ala Vaikunta Puram, and Naa Illu India. Initially, the actor resided with his family in a bungalow located in the Jubilee Hills region of Hyderabad. However, post his brother&#8217;s marriage, he shifted to the city&#8217;s outskirts, building his own house named &#8216;Blessing.&#8217;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">In his new modernized palace, the actor lives with his wife, Allu Sneha Reddy, an actor belonging to the same industry. The couple resides in the house with three significantly distinctive members. They are none other than their children Arha and Ayaan, also, not to miss out, Kazoku, their beloved pet dog. The residence is big enough to accommodate all its members and the luxuries they need. Also, the backyard is another part of the house that you can&#8217;t miss out on.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-key-features-of-allu-arjun-s-home\">Key Features of Allu Arjun\u2019s Home</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Key-Features-of-Allu-Arjuns-Home.jpg\" alt=\"Key Features of Allu Arjun\u2019s Home\" class=\"wp-image-31275\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Key-Features-of-Allu-Arjuns-Home.jpg 640w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Key-Features-of-Allu-Arjuns-Home-240x300.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /><figcaption>Source: Instagram</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The distinctive part about the celebrity home is the structure that makes it stand out. It is a box-shaped house with all amenities inside it. Besides, there is a backyard that has been specially gifted to the junior Allu by his grandfather. The structuring and designing of the house were undertaken by a firm named Aamir &amp; Hameeda Associates, with Aamir Sharma being the designer himself. The circumscribing plot that the house was built on is nothing less than two acres in its measurement. As claimed by the designer, the actor wanted his house to be a &#8220;comfortable holiday home.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Keeping his specific requirements in mind, the house was designed just the right way. Today, architecture enthusiasts drool over the structuring and detailing of the Allu Arjun house. Taking note of the modern interiors alongside convenience, the major areas of the house have been kept connected to one another for easy access. Thus, one would find the kitchen, living room, dining area, and bar right close to one another.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The overall design of the house is very minimalistic yet offers a classic modern-day look and feel. The corridor-like structure built right from the entrance leads to the living spaces. Very interestingly, an artificial grass-like pattern has been used by the designer in a wall that connects to the garden lying in the backyard of the house. Also, the swimming area holds a canopy owing to which the beautiful seating area is mostly under ignorance. Spread over 8000 Sq. Ft, the celebrity home in Hyderabad stands as a true elegance to witness.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-interesting-insights-about-allu-arjun-s-abode\">Interesting Insights About Allu Arjun\u2019s Abode</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"783\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Interesting-Insights-About-Allu-Arjuns-Abode.jpg\" alt=\"Interesting Insights About Allu Arjun\u2019s Abode\" class=\"wp-image-31277\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Interesting-Insights-About-Allu-Arjuns-Abode.jpg 640w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Interesting-Insights-About-Allu-Arjuns-Abode-245x300.jpg 245w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /><figcaption>Source: Instagram</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">It would be surprising to hear that the celeb home is constructed out of low-maintenance materials. For example, epoxy cement has been used for the in-house flooring, linking kitchen, bar counters, and several shelves in the seating areas. However, the dining area is another point of attraction in the house. It is a cemented base topped with glass, backed by white ply benches. Moreover, the benches have been made moveable to fit into the outdoor vibe.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Another specific attractive area is the bar counter. The area is coupled with bar tools in white color. On the hind side of the bar, there lies a very elegant piece of artefact which is not one. It holds a metal plank with nails on it, which functions as a bottle holder. To suit the whole minimalistic vibe of the house, its specific corners have been groomed with quirky accessories to add to the vibe and, in turn, make it look elegant.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-interiors-of-allu-arjun-house-key-facts\">Interiors of Allu Arjun House: Key Facts</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"788\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Interiors-of-Allu-Arjun-House-Key-Facts.jpg\" alt=\"Interiors of Allu Arjun House Key Facts\" class=\"wp-image-31278\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Interiors-of-Allu-Arjun-House-Key-Facts.jpg 640w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Interiors-of-Allu-Arjun-House-Key-Facts-244x300.jpg 244w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /><figcaption>Source: Instagram</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>The colors infused in each corner of the house are mostly neutrals or whites.</li><li>The house is built entirely on modern-day look and vibe</li><li>The spacious living room of the house depicts the choice of the couple</li><li>From cushions on the couch to certain other areas hold striped patterns</li><li>On the living room, one can find an ottoman with a diver too</li><li>All across the living room lies several wooden shelves with family portraits and pictures enclosed in glass</li><li>There are various seating areas in the house with a somewhat different vibe and feel. While some are more on the casual side, some others are guest friendly</li><li>The kitchen area rightly complements the overall vibe of the house. It is all adorned in whites and ivory (neutral shades here too)</li><li>For the dining area, the couple picked a wooden table with taupe chairs. A small counter close to the dining table acts as a divider between the dining and living areas.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-kid-s-corner-in-arjun-s-abode\">Kid\u2019s corner in Arjun\u2019s Abode</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The house with two kids deserves the right attention for the two. There need to be some factors present for the kids to call it home. Hence, the property beholds a vibrant nursery where the kids have seen dwellings often. The junior Allu Ayaan has a mesmerizing bedroom to his credit. It beholds subtly vibrant colors such as white and pastel blue on its walls and other corners. There lies a white cabinet to store all his play items. The actor&#8217;s love for his kids as a father is truly depicted in his public posts.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">nother item in the room is a floating wall-like shelving structure that is meant for the kid to portray his collection so far. Besides, there lies a specific television room in the house where the kids are seen spending some relaxation time. The pool, the greenery, and the plant life all around the house are other interesting nooks for the kids. The family pictures on different parts of the house shared on various social media platforms depict the bonding that the family shares with the house.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-other-prized-possessions-owned-by-allu-arjun\">Other prized possessions owned by Allu Arjun</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The south-Indian actor has spent his hard-earned money to get himself the best of all. Furthermore, several other remarkable possessions are of high value for the actor. Though he has been spotted adorning himself in luxurious and expensive clothing, there is quite some other extra spending that the actor keeps a knack for. Let&#8217;s have a look at some of them:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-a-vanity-van\">A vanity van</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">It is of no surprise that the actor owns a vanity van worth \u20b97 crores. He bought the vanity van in 2019 and named it &#8216;Falcon.&#8217; The interiors of the van are adorned in colors such as black, white, or silver. The van comprises certain symbolic features such as a giant mirror, leather seats, and many more. There is no doubt that the actor prefers style and elegance for all things equally.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-jaguar-xj-l\">Jaguar XJ L</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The actor\u2019s possession of a customized vanity van brings forth his interest in vehicles. Similarly, he has invested \u20b91.2 crores in a Jaguar XJ L. The car offers a thundering speed of 250 km/hours and is accountable for one of the most spent items for Arjun Allu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-range-rover-vogue\">Range rover vogue</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">The actor&#8217;s love for cars seems never-ending. He has been a spendthrift in this regard. One of his Instagram posts with the car and the perfect caption portrays how much of a car lover he is. It cost him about \u20b91.88 crores to \u20b9 4.03 crores approx, and hence it is definitely on the list of his prized possessions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-volvo-xc90-t8-excellence\">Volvo XC90 T8 Excellence</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">It cost him about \u20b91.30-1.35 crore to get this beast. But, his love towards his beasts keeps adding to his collection. Nevertheless, his collection is something that most enthusiasts might be drooling over.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-wrapping-up\">Wrapping Up</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">A house is often regarded as something more than just a mere dwelling place. With that, the Allu Arjun House is a significant source of inspiration for many to build their castles on. It is one of the top houses on the outskirts of Hyderabad. The house is a typical example of modern-day elegance and class spread across quite an area. Every corner of the house beholds peaceful colors that complement the overall look.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">From soft and subtle colors to amenities specifically for the kids, the property has all that to call home. It is one of the beautiful possessions for the Allu family that they take pride in. The designers have crafted it in such a way to fit into the desires of its clients rightly. No wonder why &#8216;Blessing&#8217; the house is truly a blessing in itself for the whole Allu family.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-you-might-also-like\">You Might Also Like</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-yoast-seo-related-links\"><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/bollywood-celebrities-on-a-home-buying-spree\">Bollywood Celebrities on a Home Buying Spree</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/ultimate-guide-false-ceiling-decor-ideas-for-kids-room\">The Ultimate Guide: False Ceiling D\u00e9cor Ideas For Kids\u2019 Room</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/a-sneak-peek-into-kapil-sharmas-homes-in-mumbai-and-punjab\">A Sneak Peek Into Kapil Sharma\u2019s Homes in Mumbai and Punjab</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/buying-a-home-in-bangalore-here-are-some-things-you-should-know\">Buying a home in Bangalore? Here are some things you should know</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/a-peek-into-indian-celebrity-real-estate-interests\">A Peek into Indian Celebrity Real Estate Interests</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-frequently-asked-questions-faqs\">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>\n\n\n        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>What is the worth of Allu Arjun&#8217;s house in Hyderabad?</h2>                <div>\n\t\t\t\t\t                    <p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAs a fan of the popular superstar, you would always interrogate knowing the titbits of his life. The net worth of his house in the current market is nothing less than \u20b9100 crores. The jaw-dropping interiors and exteriors of the house are worth every penny spent on it. Thus, &#8216;blessing&#8217; is i