egance make them loved by everyone. Today, he resides in a multi-crore luxurious home with his beautiful wife, two lovely children and a career graph that is skyrocketing.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-from-actor-to-columnist-twinkle-khanna-s-journey\"><strong>From Actor to Columnist- Twinkle Khanna\u2019s Journey</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Twinkle Khanna</strong> hails from a heritage generation. Her father was the superstar Rajesh Khanna and her mother is the gorgeous Dimple Kapadia. She started acting at a young age, attempting to follow in the footsteps of her parents but soon decided to quit due to several flops in her kitty. She met Akshay Kumar during a movie shoot and they dated for a while before getting married.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Over the years, she has made a mark of her own by becoming a published writer with 3 books. She also worked with the reputed architect Hafeez Contractor and became a successful interior designer herself. An opinionated feminist, she is known for her sarcasm and goofy sense of humour. Together, they make a wonderful couple who share similar interests for the most part but are also extremely unlike each other.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-how-much-does-akshay-kumar-s-juhu-home-cost-value-of-akshay-kumar-house\"><strong>How Much Does Akshay Kumar&#8217;s Juhu Home Cost? | Value of Akshay Kumar House</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Juhu is amicably nicknamed the &#8216;Beverly Hills&#8217; of Mumbai due to the presence of some of the most famous celebrities living there. This has also made the property prices, especially in prime beach locations skyrocket.<strong> Akshay Kumar&#8217;s house price in Juhu </strong>costs a whopping \u20b980 crores as per today&#8217;s rates. <strong>Twinkle Khanna </strong>has personally decorated the entire place and the tasteful and plush outcome is mainly to her credit ranging from drafting the design theme to ensuring it is finished with panache.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-interiors-decor-in-akshay-kumar-twinkle-khanna-s-hous