de in Juhu has some striking features that make it stand out. Several photoshoots and social media posts have furthermore shared these attributes with the rest of the world. Let us have a look at <strong>Akshay Kumar\u2019s Juhu house features and amenities </strong>as stated below;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"602\" height=\"401\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Picture2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-30868\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Picture2.jpg 602w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Picture2-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>A thirteen-part pendant light is located in the living room.</li><li>Their centre table has been designed by the dynamic duo Abu Jani and Sandeep Khosla</li><li>Vogue has described this house as &#8220;a lush sanctuary amidst the urban chaos&#8221;</li><li>The luxurious, yet humble abode enjoys an unrestricted view of the Juhu beach.</li><li>You can see through the orchard from the dining room through a full-length glass partition</li><li>The ground floor has a lavish walk-in wardrobe, living room and home theatre</li><li>The first floor has the master bedroom, children\u2019s rooms, guest bedroom, balcony and Twinkle&#8217;s office and a pantry</li><li>There are Italian sofas on the first floor which have been outsourced from many reputed brands.</li><li>South Indian silver sculptures and European artefacts grace the common areas.</li><li>The balcony has a daybed where the family enjoys some quality time together</li><li>Several reading corners adorn the house to suffice <strong>Twinkle Khanna</strong>&#8216;s reading cravings as she is an avid reader</li><li>The lawn outside has weather-resistant outdoor furniture which is apt for enjoying the breathtaking view of Juhu beach.</li><li>Every wall and corner of the house is tastefu