on the first two floors in the building. It has many luxurious amenities such as power backup, elevators, ample car parking, 24/7 water supply and much more. It is a gated community that adds to the safety and security of all its residents. All the apartments of this building are sea-facing and are considered to be some of the most expensive apartments in Mumbai.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Constructed by Talati and Panthaki architects, a reputed architectural duo who only works in luxury, this building has a beautiful design and fabulous finishes. While both indoor and outdoor facilities are available, Akshay Kumar&#8217;s home is complete to his and his family&#8217;s needs, so they seldom use the common amenities that the other residents of that building engage in. The average price for buying a house in this building will cost anywhere between \u20b920 crores &#8211; \u20b980 crores.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-in-and-around-his-neighbourhood-in-juhu\"><strong>In and Around his Neighbourhood in Juhu</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An iconic landmark, Juhu beach has been at the visiting end of almost every Mumbaikar and attracts tourists from all over the world. Fondly called Akki, <strong>Akshay Kumar</strong>&#8216;s home is bang on the beach where he and his lovely family enjoy undulated waves of the sea and sandy cool breeze. Juhu is home to many other stars and many have purchased properties there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Juhu is home to some of the most exotic fine-dining restaurants, bars, clubs, malls and much more. The famous Prithvi theatre is located within close vicinity of the neighbourhood along with other small theatres, giving the reputation of being the art hub of Mumbai. Bandra-Worli sea link is not too far away (around 10 minutes\u2019 drive), an architectural marvel that allows people to make it to south Mumbai from Bandra within 7 minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Shakti Kapoor, Anil Kapoor, Govinda, Sunny Deol, Hritik Roshan and many other famous personalities live in Juhu which also include affluent businessmen and their families.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Popular seven star hotels such as The Park, Sea Princess, Leela and J.W Marriott among others are also close by. The Marriott is within walking distance to the couple&#8217;s house and they often go there to wine and dine.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Reputed schools such as Jamnabai Narsee and C.P Goenka are in Juhu where many star kids study. Santacruz metro is also within close proximity and overall, makes the suburb very accessible. The popular Hare Krishna Temple is also within a distance of 3 kilometres where many people come to pray.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, numerous elite and luxe buildings are present in Juhu, mainly on the famous Juhu Tara Road. The prices for these properties are high and have gone even higher over the years.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Akshay Kumar</strong> enjoys the bliss of a fantastic property in a lush neighbourhood that is on a prime beach location. Most people can only dream of owning such homes which are luxurious and abundant. The building called Prime Beach is also home to his extended family and other famous stars. It is a beautiful property right on the beach with a stunning view amidst the clamour and chaos of the bustling Juhu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-faq-s\"><strong>FAQ&#8217;s</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>1.<strong>How many floors are there in Akshay Kumar and Twinkle Khanna&#8217;s house?</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is a two-storey duplex apartment which has large rooms on each floor. They are located on the ground and the first floor of the building and also have a large lawn and orchard that overlooks Juhu beach where many fans come in hopes of catching a glimpse of the stars.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>2.<strong>How much does Akshay Kumar&#8217;s house cost?</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Akshay Kumar</strong>&#8216;s house has been evaluated at \u20b980 crores as per today&#8217;s ongoing real estate rates.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>3.<strong>How far is the international airport from Akshay and Twinkle&#8217;s house?