            "content_text": "Needing no introduction, the very own &#8216;khiladi&#8217; of Bollywood and one of the highest-paid actors, Akshay Kumar has an uber-luxe home, matching his stature and status. A self-made man, he and his celebrity wife Twinkle Khanna own a beautiful beach front duplex apartment facing the Arabian Sea in the heart of Juhu in Mumbai, which they call home.&nbsp;\n\n\n\nOne of the most bankable stars of the industry, Akshay Kumar&#8217;s house reflects his and his wife&#8217;s elegant taste and is a popular landmark of the area as well. A reputed columnist and interior designer, his wife is also quite the celebrity, pulling a huge crowd to come to get a glimpse of her and her husband on the beach overlooked by their garden area. Not only this, situated on a prime beach location, Akshay Kumar and Twinkle Khanna&#8217;s house is a reflection of the power couple&#8217;s success, taste, charm, and luxury preferences.\n\n\n\nFrom Chef to Superstar- Akshay Kumar\u2019s Journey\n\n\n\nAkshay Kumar is one of the most bankable actors with a movie kitty of around 150, many of which were super hits. The 53 year old actor, originally named Rajiv Bhatia started off as a chef in a small restaurant in Bangkok. He engaged in martial arts and became an expert in the field shortly before the glitzy lights of Bollywood allured him to Mumbai. He failed initially and took off to Canada to pursue another career choice but the glamour of Bollywood could not keep him away and thank god for that.\n\n\n\nMet his wife Twinkle Khanna who quit the acting world years ago and went on to become a successful columnist and interior designer. Truly a power couple, their charisma and elegance make them loved by everyone. Today, he resides in a multi-crore luxurious home with his beautiful wife, two lovely children and a career graph that is skyrocketing.\n\n\n\nFrom Actor to Columnist- Twinkle Khanna\u2019s Journey\n\n\n\nTwinkle Khanna hails from a heritage generation. Her father was the superstar Rajesh Khanna and her mother is the gorgeous Dimple Kapadia. She started acting at a young age, attempting to follow in the footsteps of her parents but soon decided to quit due to several flops in her kitty. She met Akshay Kumar during a movie shoot and they dated for a while before getting married.\n\n\n\nOver the years, she has made a mark of her own by becoming a published writer with 3 books. She also worked with the reputed architect Hafeez Contractor and became a successful interior designer herself. An opinionated feminist, she is known for her sarcasm and goofy sense of humour. Together, they make a wonderful couple who share similar interests for the most part but are also extremely unlike each other.\n\n\n\nHow Much Does Akshay Kumar&#8217;s Juhu Home Cost? | Value of Akshay Kumar House\n\n\n\nJuhu is amicably nicknamed the &#8216;Beverly Hills&#8217; of Mumbai due to the presence of some of the most famous celebrities living there. This has also made the property prices, especially in prime beach locations skyrocket. Akshay Kumar&#8217;s house price in Juhu costs a whopping \u20b980 crores as per today&#8217;s rates. Twinkle Khanna has personally decorated the entire place and the tasteful and plush outcome is mainly to her credit ranging from drafting the design theme to ensuring it is finished with panache.\n\n\n\nInteriors &amp; Decor in Akshay Kumar &amp; Twinkle Khanna\u2019s House in Juhu\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nDesigned by Twinkle Khanna an influential feminist, this mesmerising home is the epitome of all-things-smart. This two-level bungalow has a large pond which acts as the centrepiece of the living room. The ground floor has a large walk-in wardrobe, a lavish kitchen and a home theatre whereas the upper floor has the master bedroom, with a sophisticated grey interiors colour theme.\n\n\n\nA lot in Akshay Kumar&#8217;s house\u2019s interior and decor theme has a touch of nature, giving it an organic vibe. A Mango tree has been planted in their orchard which reminds Twinkle of her superstar dad, Rajesh Khanna. The orchard is surrounded by a beautiful green lawn with blue being the dominant colour there. The rest of the house is dabbled in grey, beige and brown, encompassing everything, from the furniture to the walls.\n\n\n\nFurthermore, the house is full of personal mementos such as photographs of the family, souvenirs from their travels, artefacts and much more. Apart from the lush interior theme, the family enjoys an enviable view of the famous Juhu beach where sometimes, you can spot the couple taking a late-night walk.\n\n\n\nMore on Akshay Kumar&#8217;s Duplex Apartment\n\n\n\nThe actor&#8217;s plush abode in Juhu has some striking features that make it stand out. Several photoshoots and social media posts have furthermore shared these attributes with the rest of the world. Let us have a look at Akshay Kumar\u2019s Juhu house features and amenities as stated below;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nA thirteen-part pendant light is located in the living room.Their centre table has been designed by the dynamic duo Abu Jani and Sandeep KhoslaVogue has described this house as &#8220;a lush sanctuary amidst the urban chaos&#8221;The luxurious, yet humble abode enjoys an unrestricted view of the Juhu beach.You can see through the orchard from the dining room through a full-length glass partitionThe ground floor has a lavish walk-in wardrobe, living room and home theatreThe first floor has the master bedroom, children\u2019s rooms, guest bedroom, balcony and Twinkle&#8217;s office and a pantryThere are Italian sofas on the first floor which have been outsourced from many reputed brands.South Indian silver sculptures and European artefacts grace the common areas.The balcony has a daybed where the family enjoys some quality time togetherSeveral reading corners adorn the house to suffice Twinkle Khanna&#8216;s reading cravings as she is an avid readerThe lawn outside has weather-resistant outdoor furniture which is apt for enjoying the breathtaking view of Juhu beach.Every wall and corner of the house is tastefully adorned with sculptures, photographs and artefacts of renowned artists and personal picturesThe family grows their own fruits and vegetables in a vegetation patch draped into the orchardThere is a pond in the garden that has a Buddha head rising statueThe centrepiece of the living room consists of a beautiful water body in the form of a pondThe entire duplex apartment is pet friendly as the family has a wonderful dogHe lives in a building called Prime Beach building.\n\n\n\nPalatial Properties Owned By Akshay Kumar\n\n\n\nOver the years, owing to his success, Akshay Kumar is the proud owner of many properties ranging from investment options to holiday homes and much more. Both in India as well as abroad, the superstar has some enviable properties across the world. Some of Akshay Kumar&#8217;s properties are stated below.\n\n\n\nSea Facing duplex in Juhu, Mumbai, IndiaPortuguese style home in Goa, IndiaFour apartments in Andheri, Mumbai.Spacious bungalow in MauritiusA superior hill and an estate in CanadaApartments and villas in Canada\n\n\n\nIn addition to the ones mentioned above, he has many properties including flats, apartments, villas, and independent houses all over the world which showcase his staggering wealth.\n\n\n\nMore About Prime Beach Duplex Apartment | Where Akshay Kumar Currently Resides\n\n\n\nOffering skilfully designed apartments of varying configurations, owing to a house in Prime Beach is a thing of prestige. Akshay Kumar&#8216;s house is on the first two floors in the building. It has many luxurious amenities such as power backup, elevators, ample car parking, 24/7 water supply and much more. It is a gated community that adds to the safety and security of all its residents. All the apartments of this building are sea-facing and are considered to be some of the most expensive apartments in Mumbai.\n\n\n\nConstructed by Talati and Panthaki architects, a reputed architectural duo who only works in luxury, this building has a beautiful design and fabulous finishes. While both indoor and outdoor facilities are available, Akshay Kumar&#8217;s home is complete to his and his family&#8217;s needs, so they seldom use the common amenities that the other residents of that building engage in. The average price for buying a house in this building will cost anywhere between \u20b920 crores &#8211; \u20b980 crores.\n\n\n\nIn and Around his Neighbourhood in Juhu\n\n\n\nAn iconic landmark, Juhu beach has been at the visiting end of almost every Mumbaikar and attracts tourists from all over the world. Fondly called Akki, Akshay Kumar&#8216;s home is bang on the beach where he and his lovely family enjoy undulated waves of the sea and sandy cool breeze. Juhu is home to many other stars and many have purchased properties there.\n\n\n\nJuhu is home to some of the most exotic fine-dining restaurants, bars, clubs, malls and much more. The famous Prithvi theatre is located within close vicinity of the neighbourhood along with other small theatres, giving the reputation of being the art hub of Mumbai. Bandra-Worli sea link is not too far away (around 10 minutes\u2019 drive), an architectural marvel that allows people to make it to south Mumbai from Bandra within 7 minutes.\n\n\n\nShakti Kapoor, Anil Kapoor, Govinda, Sunny Deol, Hritik Roshan and many other famous personalities live in Juhu which also include affluent businessmen and their families.\n\n\n\nPopular seven star hotels such as The Park, Sea Princess, Leela and J.W Marriott among others are also close by. The Marriott is within walking distance to the couple&#8217;s house and they often go there to wine and dine.\n\n\n\nReputed schools such as Jamnabai Narsee and C.P Goenka are in Juhu where many star kids study. Santacruz metro is also within close proximity and overall, makes the suburb very accessible. The popular Hare Krishna Temple is also within a distance of 3 kilometres where many people come to pray.\n\n\n\nLastly, numerous elite and luxe buildings are present in Juhu, mainly on the famous Juhu Tara Road. The prices for these properties are high and have gone even higher over the years.\n\n\n\nAkshay Kumar enjoys the bliss of a fantastic property in a lush neighbourhood that is on a prime beach location. Most people can only dream of owning such homes which are luxurious and abundant. The building called Prime Beach is also home to his extended family and other famous stars. It is a beautiful property right on the beach with a stunning view amidst the clamour and chaos of the bustling Juhu.\n\n\n\nFAQ&#8217;s\n\n\n\n1.How many floors are there in Akshay Kumar and Twinkle Khanna&#8217;s house?\n\n\n\nIt is a two-storey duplex apartment which has large rooms on each floor. They are located on the ground and the first floor of the building and also have a large lawn and orchard that overlooks Juhu beach where many fans come in hopes of catching a glimpse of the stars.\n\n\n\n2.How much does Akshay Kumar&#8217;s house cost?\n\n\n\nAkshay Kumar&#8216;s house has been evaluated at \u20b980 crores as per today&#8217;s ongoing real estate rates.\n\n\n\n3.How far is the international airport from Akshay and Twinkle&#8217;s house?\n\n\n\nChhatrapati Shivaji is the nearest international airport and is at a distance of around 5 kilometres from Akshay Kumar&#8216;s home. It takes around 15-20 minutes by car to get there one way.\n\n\n\n4.Does any other known celebrity live within the immediate neighbourhood?\n\n\n\nAkshay Kumar&#8216;s mother and sister live in the same building and recently, Hritik Roshan has purchased an apartment in the same building.\n\n\n\n5.What is the name of the building in which Akshay Kumar resides?\n\n\n\nThe name of the building in which Akshay Kumar and Twinkle Khanna live is called Prime Beach building.\nThe post A Sneak Peek into Multi-crore Duplex Apartment of Akshay Kumar appeared first on Real Es