            "content_html": "<p><strong><em>Bollywood celebrities seem to be on a roll as they are on an incessant home-buying spree amidst the pandemic. Well, B-town is a place of glamour and luxury and so is the actors\u2019 king-size lifestyles. From their high-end branded clothes to their posh houses they live in, everything about them is ultra-luxurious and fancy. To keep you updated with the buzz around Bollywood celebrities\u2019 homes and where they reside, Square Yards brings to you a list of Bollywood actors who have made big-ticket real estate investments recently.</em></strong></p>\n<p>After Hrithik Roshan, Janhvi Kapoor, Alia Bhatt, reports are making the rounds that Ajay Devgn, Arjun Kapoor and Amitabh Bachchan have made ultra-luxurious, big-ticket <a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/a-peek-into-indian-celebrity-real-estate-interests\">real estate investments</a>. Let\u2019s take a sneak peek into these.</p>\n<h4><em><strong>Also Read- </strong><strong><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/bollywood-celebrity-homes-that-spurred-a-boom-in-mumbais-luxury-market\">Bollywood Celebrity Homes That Spurred a Boom in Mumbai\u2019s Luxury Market</a></strong></em></h4>\n<h3><strong>Ajay Devgn buys a luxurious bungalow worth </strong><strong>\u20b9</strong><strong>60 Crore</strong></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_30586\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30586\" style=\"width: 434px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-30586\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/navbharat-times-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Ajay Devgn buys a luxurious bungalow worth \u20b960 Crore\" width=\"434\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/navbharat-times-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/navbharat-times.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 434px) 100vw, 434px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-30586\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><em>Source: navbharattimes.com</em></strong></figcaption></figure></p></blockquote>\n<p>The box office superstar, Ajay Devgn is one of the most bankable actors of Bollywood today. After all, in 2019 he was featured in Forbes India\u2019s Celebrity 100 list and back then he had bagged the 12th spot with annual earnings of \u20b994 crore. His massive net worth mirrors his ultra-rich lifestyle that has been nothing but super luxurious with plush abodes, pricey cars and other high-end possessions.</p>\n<p>His most recent purchase is an \u00a0opulent \u00a0bungalow in Juhu worth a whopping \u20b960 crore, a hefty price, indeed.\u00a0The \u00a0exquisite bungalow sprawls across 590 Sq. Yds. and it is in the vicinity of his current residence Shakti.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_30590\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30590\" style=\"width: 372px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-30590\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/83099474-300x158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"195\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/83099474-300x158.jpg 300w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/83099474.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 372px) 100vw, 372px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-30590\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em><strong>Source: timesofindia.com</strong></em></figcaption></figure></p></blockquote>\n<p>Well, it seems like Juhu is the new vibrant hotspot and preferred prime locality for Bollywood celebrities as it already hosts a dozen of other celebrities like Alia Bhatt, Amitabh Bachchan, Hrithik Roshan, etc. However, Ajay\u2019s new purchase is already making fans curious as the renovation work of the bungalow has begun.</p>\n<p>Some of the \u00a0other high-end priced possessions owned by Ajay Devgn include &#8211; a private jet, \u20b954 crore luxurious bungalow in London, \u20b96.5 crore Rolls Royce Cullinan, \u20b91.5 crore Maserati car and many more.</p>\n<h3><strong>Amitabh Bachchan buys a palatial apartment worth </strong><strong>\u20b9</strong><strong>31 Crore in Andheri</strong></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_30592\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30592\" style=\"width: 297px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-30592\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/62520interesting2520facts2520about2520Amitabh2520Bachchan25E225802599s2520Mumbai2520home-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"297\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/62520interesting2520facts2520about2520Amitabh2520Bachchan25E225802599s2520Mumbai2520home-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/62520interesting2520facts2520about2520Amitabh2520Bachchan25E225802599s2520Mumbai2520home-682x1024.jpg 682w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/62520interesting2520facts2520about2520Amitabh2520Bachchan25E225802599s2520Mumbai2520home-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/62520interesting2520facts2520about2520Amitabh2520Bachchan25E225802599s2520Mumbai2520home.jpg 899w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-30592\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em><strong>Source: vogue.in</strong></em></figcaption></figure></p></blockquote>\n<p>Megastar Amitabh Bachchan has once again made \u00a0headlines and this time for splurging on a brand new duplex apartment worth \u20b931 Crore. Located in the heart of Mumbai, Amitabh Bachchan has bought a sprawling duplex apartment that spreads over an area of 5,704 Sq. Ft. in Andheri, the western suburbs of Mumbai.</p>\n<p>According to reports, he bought the property in December 2020 by paying a stamp duty of \u20b962 lakh, which is 2 percent of \u20b931 crore but got it registered in April 2021. Due to the stamp duty cut waiver offered by the Maharashtra state government last year, a lot of big-ticket real estate deals had taken place between September 2020 and March 2021.</p>\n<blockquote><p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-30596\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-27-1280x720-1-300x169.png\" alt=\"Bollywood Celebrity: Amitabh Bachchan Home\" width=\"421\" height=\"237\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-27-1280x720-1-300x169.png 300w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-27-1280x720-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-27-1280x720-1-768x432.png 768w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-27-1280x720-1.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 421px) 100vw, 421px\" /></p></blockquote>\n<p>Big B\u2019s grandeur apartment is situated on the 27th and 28th floor of the building and the icing on the cake is that it comes with six mechanised parking slots. Apart from the new Andheri apartment, Big B is the proud owner of many multi-crore properties like Jalsa, Janak, Prateeksha, Vatsa.</p>\n<p>According to several reports, filmmaker Anand L Rai and Bollywood celebrity Sunny Leone have also bought a luxe duplex apartment in the same complex. Actress Sunny Leone sealed the deal of 4,365 Sq. Ft apartment for \u20b916 crore and while, Anand L Rai bought a duplex apartment in the same complex for over \u20b925 crore.</p>\n<h3><strong>Bollywood celebrity Arjun Kapoor buys a sea-facing 4-BHK apartment worth </strong><strong>\u20b9</strong><strong>20 Crore</strong></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_30598\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30598\" style=\"width: 418px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-30598\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Arjun-Kapoor-purchases-a-rich-4-BHK-ocean-confronting-house-in-Mumbai-300x258.png\" alt=\"Arjun Kapoor Purchases a 4 BHK apartment\" width=\"418\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Arjun-Kapoor-purchases-a-rich-4-BHK-ocean-confronting-house-in-Mumbai-300x258.png 300w, https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Arjun-Kapoor-purchases-a-rich-4-BHK-ocean-confronting-house-in-Mumbai.png 625w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 418px) 100vw, 418px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-30598\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em><strong>Source: Pinterest</strong></em></figcaption></figure></p></blockquote>\n<p>Arjun Kapoor has recently completed ten years in the film industry. On the work front, he is grabbing attention and garnering praises for his last performance in the film Sandeep Aur Pinky Faraar. Basking in the success of his last film, Arjun Kapoor has gifted himself a swanky sea-facing 4 BHK \u00a0apartment near his ladylove Malika Arora\u2019s abode in one of Mumbai\u2019s posh localities.</p>\n<p>Arjun Kapoor\u2019s new villa offers amenities that justify the price of his newly purchased apartment such as four personalized sea-facing capsule elevators that will drop you right to your villa, private pool, gym, library, yoga deck, open caf\u00e9, play area, business lounge, mini-golf course, spa and a pet corner.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_30599\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30599\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-30599\" src=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/download.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood celebrities' sea-facing apartment\" width=\"535\" height=\"300\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-30599\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em><strong>Source: india.com</strong></em></figcaption></figure></p></blockquote>\n<p>The picturesque and breathtaking view of Mumbai\u2019s skyline and Bandra-Worli sea link is seen from Arjun\u2019s extravagant 4 BHK apartment. The high-rise building has 81 sky villas and each villa consists of \u00a0massive 4 bedrooms which come with a private pool on the outdoor deck, spacious closet space and balcony. Isn\u2019t this a dream home?</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, in December 2020, his little step-sister Janhvi Kapoor had bought an expensive luxurious apartment in Juhu. Janhvi\u2019s luxurious apartment is worth \u20b939 crores which sprawls across three floors and is located in one of the most lavish suburban areas of the city.</p>\n<p><em><b>Real estate has proven to be the go-to-investment avenue for the Bollywood celebrities during these turbulent times. Let\u2019s see who all join the bandwagon in the upcoming months.</b></em></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/bollywood-celebrities-on-a-home-buying-spree\">Bollywood Celebrities on a Home Buying Spree</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog\">Real Estate News</a>.</p>\n",
