            "content_html": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Widely known for her comic roles in Bollywood movies and being a judge on various comedy shows, Archana Puran Singh is a name that needs no introduction. Well, Singh and her actor-husband, Parmeet Sethi\u2019s majestic bungalow is gaining eye-balls and doing rounds on the Internet. Let us take a virtual tour of Archana Puran Singh House, beautifully designed Madh Island bungalow.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Archana Puran Singh is popular for being the judge on <em>The Kapil Sharma Show</em> and known for her jolly nature, both onscreen and offscreen. She has acted in some of the greatest A-listed Bollywood movies of all times, like Kuch Kuch Hota Hai, Mohabbatein, Kick and Raja Hindustani. Singh has shared screen space with leading B-town actors, including Akshay Kumar, Aamir Khan, Shah Rukh Khan, Amitabh Bachchan, Salman Khan and many others. She was also a part of the famous TV serial Shrimaan Shrimati.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">While most Mumbaikars were locked up in their matchbox-sized apartments amidst the COVID-19 outbreak, Archana Puran Singh and Parmeet Sethi enjoyed spending some quality family time at their dreamy residence. However, the lockdown did not stop Archana from entertaining her fans. She kept her fans hooked to her Instagram handle by sharing adorable, funny pictures and videos of her family, housekeeping staff and pets. Along with that, we also got a close look at the lavish property owned by the couple that makes us completely mesmerised. Well, it sure made us envy them a bit, but looking at how hard they have worked in the entertainment industry for decades, they truly deserve all these luxuries. It is fair to say that even some of the greatest Bollywood celebrities cannot afford to have such a luxurious life as <strong>Archana Puran Singh</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What is the view from Archana Puran Singh House &amp; balcony?</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Kuch Kuch Hota Hai actress shared an Instagram video showing us the view from her balcony that is simply the star of her property. The view of refreshing lush greenery all around with high-rise buildings in the background is a treat to the eyes, and fans could not stop gushing over it. A closer look at her balcony view highlights the stunning white patio set, adding to the scenic beauty. Singh further mentions that she likes to enjoy her alone time sitting on her balcony and getting in some cool breeze when it is too hot to go outside.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Archana Puran Singh&#8217;s Lush Green Lawn</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Behind the Singh-Sethi&nbsp;bungalow, they have a lush garden with a plethora of plants and trees, vibrant flowers and benches. Singh shared a video showing Parmeet and her son spending quality time with their adorable dog named Drama in their beautiful garden. While Singh likes to sit, sip and chat with her 90-year-old mother, Sethi and the kids prefer to work it out hard in the stunning garden at the same time.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Plush Garden at Archana Puran Singh\u2019s Property</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Archana Puran Singh&nbsp;and&nbsp;Parmeet Sethi&nbsp;own a very spacious property that is no less than a resort. Their&nbsp;Madh Island&nbsp;residence has a wide and long walkway in the garden area filled with lovely lush green plants. The paved path is perfect for morning and evening walks. Singh also gave us a virtual tour of her beautiful garden through an Instagram post where she was seen walking around the lush garden accompanied by their cute dog, Drama. All we could think is, who would not like to reside here?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In some of Singh&#8217;s IG videos, we can see another small garden adjoining the lavish one. This garden seems to be devoted to growing vegetables, tomatoes, brinjal, capsicum, to name a few. Adding to that, Singh&#8217;s backyard is filled with trees of fruits like coconut, plum, papaya, mango, etc. It shows Singh and Sethi&#8217;s love and passion for gardening and nature. A glimpse of the fresh produce from their garden is seen in some of her videos.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Archana Puran Singh\u2019s Property: The Front Entrance</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Out of the many videos shared by&nbsp;Archana Puran Singh&nbsp;on her Instagram handle, one video shows a sneak peek of her stunning&nbsp;bungalow&nbsp;from outside. In this video, her mother was waving to her from the grand front stoop. It has a gated entrance with a huge doorway. The interiors seemed aesthetically pleasing and definitely well-lit with striking chandeliers. The stunning french windows and bougainvillaea plant give it a complete royal residence look.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp;A royal affair in the living room</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Archana Puran Singh&nbsp;and&nbsp;Parmeet Singh&#8217;s lavish&nbsp;bungalow<strong>&nbsp;</strong>has a mesmerising living room. Furnished with a white modish couch, trendy lights, and a centrally placed chandelier, Singh&#8217;s living room is what dreams are made of. Also, one cannot miss the mirrors on the walls and wall paintings in the background that add to the room&#8217;s royal aura.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Luxe Master Bedroom</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Archana Puran Singh&#8217;s fans get a glimpse of the luxurious and spacious master bedroom of her&nbsp;bungalow&nbsp;time and again through her IG videos. Singh&#8217;s bedroom gives classy Boho vibes with a simple pastel palette, clean, white cotton linen and a wicker-designed bed. The room decor shows the star&#8217;s love for subtle colours like white and baby pink. One of the videos where Singh&#8217;s domestic help, Bhagyashree, was in the limelight- the video highlighted the room&#8217;s beautifully done modern furniture like the bedroom chair and table set, recliner chair, artwork on the wall and the hanging lights. In another picture posted by Singh, we see her other canine friend &#8216;Patch&#8217; resting under the bed like a boss.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The actress left her fans spellbound with her meticulously modern designed room interior. Adorned with a comfy white L-shaped lounge sofa set, white mirrored closets behind it and beige coloured curtains, the room has an austere look. Adding to the room&#8217;s grandeur was the metallic gold furniture and door handles, a centrally placed stylish hanging ceiling lamp and the huge flatscreen TV mounted on the wall.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The Lobby Area</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In one of the IG videos shared by Singh, we catch the cute banter between Bhagyashree and another member of the housekeeping staff, Raj. We also notice the beautiful lobby area just outside Singh and Sethi&#8217;s luxurious master bedroom. It has a formal table and revolving chair set-up. A notice board is also placed on the side, and it might be the space for work-related discussions. It leads to the staircase with a spandrel decorated with artistic paintings, comfy chairs and lamps, giving it a classy look altogether. The video also depicts the friendly relation Singh, and her family members have with their housekeeping staff.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What\u2019s the Buzz around their Pet Room?</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Recently,&nbsp;Archana Puran Singh&nbsp;posted a lovely Instagram picture where she introduced her fans to their two adorable pets, Patch and Drama, who love lounging around the royal bungalow. They were lazing around in a classic white and gold coloured room with pink-grey draping, white rugs and modern furniture. With an old school four-post wooden bed, a mounted wall TV set and a blue moving comfy recliner chair- is the perfect place to unwind at the end of a long day. Singh wanted to clear the misconception among her fans that her dogs do not have any place to chill inside their home. The picture shows Patch lazing on his cosy rug while Drama is literally chilling on the cold floor, licking and drooling all over. It shows the couple&#8217;s love for their pets.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The Modular Kitchen</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Singh&#8217;s&nbsp;Madh Island residence has a huge kitchen space, as seen in one of her Instagram videos featuring Bhagyashree and her son. The kitchen area is as elegant as the rest of the bungalow, with white cabinets and round-patterned wall tiles. The ceiling lights highlight this space, and we cannot get our eyes off them. The area is spacious enough, allowing proper air circulation with a designed kitchen chimney. It also has a small TV mounted on the wall to keep them entertained while cooking.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Instagram-Worthy Home D\u00e9cor</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Along with their acting skills, the Singh-Sethi couple also seems to have a good eye for design and architecture, as seen from the nook and corners of their&nbsp;Madh Island property. The interiors of their house are as wonderful and beautiful as the garden outside. In one of the videos shared by Singh, where she thanked her fans for their love, support and positivity, we caught a glimpse of her stunning interiors with a mix of subtle colours. The soft baby pink and grey curtains, the beautiful lampshade by her side and the white vase with lovely pink flowers compliment each other well and give the room a serene look. Singh further mentioned how she does not mind being called old and takes it very casually.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Archana Puran Singh Family: Sharing Festive Vibes</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In another IG video posted during Diwali, we see Singh celebrate and share some cheerful moments with Parmeet, her mother, her sons and the housekeeping staff at their lavish abode. Adding to the completely classy look is the stylish wall lamp, beige sofa set, large windows with flowy white curtains and the big artwork in the background.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The Singh-Sethi Couple like to Keep it Cool</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As&nbsp;Madh Island is too close to the sea, the Singh-Sethi residence might be humid during summers. To counter this, Archana and Parmeet try to maintain a cosy, easy-breezy and serene set-up at their place. The dream house is perfectly balanced with whites, powder blue and just the right accents of gold. We also notice several houseplants at the celebrity&#8217;s bungalow that help maintain the cool.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Movie Nights at Archana Puran Singh&#8217;s Posh Abode</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of Singh&#8217;s Instagram posts shows the huge flatscreen TV mounted on the wall.&nbsp;Archana Puran Singh&#8217;s family&nbsp;probably chills here together during a movie night. The all-white TV bench paired with the golden-white wall lamp gives it a complete royal look.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Singh-Sethi&nbsp;bungalow<strong>&nbsp;</strong>is a class apart with loads of classic white upholstery and furnishing and no loud colour, giving a royal look throughout. Maintaining such an enormous property with eye-catching interiors would most definitely be difficult, but the couple has proved to do a tremendous job at it. Singh and Sethi&#8217;s plush&nbsp;Madh Island&nbsp;property has aced the residence game undoubtedly and has given us some major house goals. Living at such a majestic and luxurious residence would be a dream come true for many of us.</p>\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\n\n        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>How old is Archana Puran Singh?</h2>                <div>\n\t\t\t\t\t                    <p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tArchana Puran Singh was born on 26 September 1962 in Dehradun and is 58 years old.                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\t        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>How many children do Archana Puran Singh and Parmeet Sethi have?</h2>                <div>\n\t\t\t\t\t                    <p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tArchana Puran Singh and Parmeet Sethi have two sons named Ayushmann Sethi and Aaryamann Sethi.                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\t        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>How much is Parmeet Sethi\u2019s net worth?</h2>                <div>\n\t\t\t\t\t                    <p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tParmeet Sethi\u2019s net worth was around 1 million to 5 million dollars during 2019.                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\t        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>What does Parmeet Sethi do?</h2>                <div>\n\t\t\t\t\t                    <p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tParmeet Sethi has acted in several Bollywood hits, from Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge (1995) to Dil Dhadakne Do (2015). Currently, he has made his mark on OTT platforms by acting in web series like Special OPS and Hundred.                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\t        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>How much does Archana Puran Singh charge per episode of The Kapil Sharma Show?</h2>                <div>\n\t\t\t\t\t                    <p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tArchana Puran Singh reportedly charges INR 10 lakh per episode of The Kapil Sharma Show. Singh 