n\u2019t be expecting anything less.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">One of the luxurious houses in\u00a0<strong>Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad</strong>, is owned by the\u00a0<strong>Mahesh Babu family</strong>. The exteriors of the house are surely jaw-dropping. It is subtle but grand in look with white and grey walls and door-size sliding glass balcony windows. It matches well with the lush green garden on one side and a parking space on the other side.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">This\u00a0<strong>Hyderabad property\u00a0</strong>has an indoor swimming pool, open spaces, a cozy study room, gymnasium, green gardens, a private office for Mahesh. In addition, the actor and his wife, Namrata Shirodkar, have customized other spots in the house like the living room, the puja room, the children&#8217;s room, etc., according to the tastes of the family.\u00a0</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Every corner of the house screams luxury and comfort. What makes it best? Every element is quite subtle and soothing. We don&#8217;t see bright or vibrant colours inside the house. Shades of beige, brown, white, etc., dominate the walls, furniture, etc., but they are well contrasted yet matched with each other.\u00a0</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Mahesh Babu Family:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Mahesh Babu is the son of a Telugu actor and director, Krishna. Carrying on his father&#8217;s legacy, Mahesh started acting in films from childhood and has been loved as an actor since then. He met Namrata Shirodkar on one of the film sets in 2000, and after dating for a couple of years, they got married in 2005. Since then, the duo has been setting couple-goals. Amidst their ambitious career, they have remained loyal and dedicated to each other and have succeeded in building up a luxurious life for themselves. They are doting parents to a son, and a daughter, and their family is strongly bound by love, culture, and laughter. The family also includes two pet dogs \u2013 Nubo and Pluto.\u00a0</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">As they all are avid social media users, they keep dropping snaps from bits and corners of the house. Thanks to the pets, we get a clear view of the open garden in the house. The lush green grass is well synchronized with the trees and plants of different shapes and sizes. Sitting arrangements are made on one side of the garden. The floor is laid with grey wooden planks. There is a white marble table in the center which is surrounded by matching white sofa sets. The whole arrangement stands in perfect contrast to the dark green trees in the background.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">In another snap, we see a different sitting arrangement by the side of the garden. The flooring is the same, but we see wooden plank benches. This again matches well with the lush green background. Varieties of plants and trees find their space in the garden, and hence, together, they put up a beautiful background with different shades of green. It is the best play area for the pets and the children, but it could also be a perfect tea spot for the family on a cozy evening.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Mahesh Babu Kids:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Mahesh Babu and Namrata Shirodkar have been blessed with a son, Gautam Ghattamaneni, and a daughter, Sitara Ghattamaneni. The kids have doting parents, and they seem to enjoy all the love and attention showered on them. Mahesh Babu and Namrata Shirodkar, through their love for their children, multiply the comfort and protection of their house in their lives.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">In a few photos of Mahesh and Namrata with their kids, we get glimpses of their house. In a snap, which seems like one corner of the living room, there is a huge glass window with white curtains. There is a one-seater brown leather sofa just in front of the window. A wooden cabinet behind the couch and the shade of wood match the shade of the leather. The floor is wooden, again matching the shade of the cabinet and the sofa. To bring out a contrasting effect, there is a light brown carpet on the floor. The carpet successfully breaks the monotony of the browns and also matches with the curtain behind.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">A huge glass wall shields the entrance from the garden into the house, and this area has another sitting arrangement overlooking the garden. There are small center tables in black which are surrounded by easy chairs of a light brown shade. There is another sofa set with brown arm-rests and ash grey cushions. They look super comfortable and would make anyone want to sink into them on a windy evening.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The children&#8217;s room is going to make every child envy Gautam and Sitara. Disney characters are painted on the wall with a white bed standing in perfect contrast to the wall. The curtains in the room are printed in different colours, and they match the colourful characters on the wall. The bed, on the other hand, matches the rest of the walls in the room. All in all, the children&#8217;s section is colourful and beautifully coordinated with each other.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Mahesh and Namrata spend a lot of time with their children. The area where Mahesh plays video games with his son is spacious. It gives a broader view of the hallway. There is a TV on a dark chocolate colour cabinet. The floor is again wooden. Other doors in the house are all of the same dark chocolate colour. But for a change, pink colour sofas are present in this area. Surprisingly, they don&#8217;t look out of place. Rather they enhance the beauty of the area.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The swimming pool overlooks the garden through a glass window. It has stairs leading into it on the opposite end. The wall above the pool is grey, and the lighting is subtle, which makes the water in the pool shine and look brighter.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Namrata Shirodkar family:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Namrata was born in a Marathi-speaking family, but she became famous for some of her roles in Bollywood. She quit acting because she wanted to marry Mahesh Babu and she is a proud mother and an excellent wife.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">She gave glimpses of the puja room in the house. It is small but well-lit and spaced out. There is a white marble temple against a golden wall. On either side of the temple are glass windows overlooking the outer spaces. The floor is white too, and it serves well with the purpose of the place, adding to the serenity and peace.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">As Gautam and Sitara celebrated their birthdays, Namrata gave glimpses of some other corners of the house. Where the table is golden, the walls are decorated with paintings. The chairs are beige. The floor and walls are white. The hall is subtly lit with golden lights, which creates a beautiful ambience. To break the monotony of the whites and beige, all the doors and painting frames are dark chocolate.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Memories are an essential part of human lives. Therefore, having a memory wall in a house is fair. The memory wall in Mahesh and Namrata&#8217;s house is white. It has a good number of photo frames. There is a double seater black sofa just in front of the memory wall on a light printed carpet. This is the best place in the house to relax and reminisce about the good old times.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Namrata Shirodkar Property:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The combined net worth of Mahesh Babu and Namrata Shirodkar is approximately 100 crores. It boosts their king-size living. The working space in the house is appropriate for a working environment, with a white table and a matching white working chair. The setup stands in contrast to the dark brown cabinet in the background, a perfect place for storing books and files.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Reading is for everyone. Comfortable reading space is what facilitates good reading habits. The reading space in this house of\u00a0<strong>Jubilee Hills</strong>\u00a0has a comfortable grey-coloured sofa with a small side table. The cushions, the side table, and the cabinet behind are in different shades of brown and black, while the wall behind is olive green.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The living room is of utmost importance in every house. Not to mention again, but the living room of Mahesh and Namrata\u2019s house is luxurious, cozy, and well-designed. The home theatre is set against a light shade of wallpaper and the cabinet is a dark shade of brown, while the floor is a light shade of brown. There is a printed carpet on the floor and the sofa set is in the shade of beige which mixes well with the ambience.\u00a0</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><u><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Other corners in the property</span></u><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Fitness is important, and hence, the gymnasium is well-equipped with all the necessary machines for home-workout. There is a huge television on one wall. Another wall has a poster of Mahesh Babu with an inspirational quote written. It is well-lit and overlooks the outer space through a glass window again.\u00a0</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The sofa, the couch, the walls, and the carpet are all in the shades of beige. To break the monotony, a dark coloured center table is present, along with brightly printed cushions.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">There is another open space inside the house that looks like a division between two house sections. The floor is marbled. There are plants on both sides of the space. The two sections of the house are connected by a bridge that overlooks the marble floor beneath. But this area is again a good play space for the pets.</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><u><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Conclusion</span></u></strong><strong><u><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">\u00a0</span></span></u></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">We keep getting glimpses of the house now and then through various social media posts. Every corner of the house is decorated beautifully. Nothing is vibrant, yet nothing is dull. This house uses a smart combination of lighting and colour contrasts to bring out a rich and luxurious look.\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The best thing is that every family member\u2019s requirements and tastes are met. If there is an office for the elders, then the children have their separate rooms. The entertainment section is kept separate from the video games section, hence no interruption to anyone. The reading space is there to preach knowledge, while the puja area is there to preach culture.\u00a0</span><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Who would need anything else if there is an open garden with several comfortable sitting areas? It could fit any mood, weather, and it is surely the best hangout spot in the house.</span></p>\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\n\n        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>What is the worth of Mahesh Babu\u2019s house in Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad?</h2>                <div>\n\t\t\t\t\t                    <p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tMahesh Babu and his wife Namrata Shirodkar\u2019s hou