            "content_text": "A house is more than simply a place to live; it encapsulates all of life&#8217;s joys and sorrows, and it echoes all of the past&#8217;s splendours. This is what makes it a home. It doesn&#8217;t matter if it&#8217;s ours or someone else&#8217;s. But, when someone else is a Bollywood superstar (Kiara Advani), the house takes on a whole new meaning. It encapsulates the opulence and glamour that surrounds superstars.\nWhen we think of celebrity homes, we immediately think of the lavish, luxurious, spacious and well-decorated bungalows with an undeniable extravagance. Whether you&#8217;re seeking design ideas or just fantasising about your ultimate ideal home, some celeb homes are a great place to start. The efforts of designers and architects who work with them are immense, and they go above and beyond to make celebrities\u2019 abodes as extraordinary and beautiful as possible. Some of the best and the most popular Bollywood celebrities&#8217; homes are Mannat, the residence of Shahrukh Khan, Jalsa and Pratiksha of Amitabh Bachan, Salman Khan&#8217;s Galaxy Heights and the list goes on. Whenever tourists arrive in Mumbai, it is almost always the case that they visit these iconic homes and treat themselves to a peak from outside. It has almost become a tradition for people to look up to their success and admire their ultra-luxurious abodes. Today, let\u2019s take a virtual tour of the talented actress, Kiara Advani\u2019s brand new apartment nestled in the suburb Mahalaxmi area of Mumbai.\nEven though she is fairly new in the fraternity, her achievement speaks volume about her talent and flair. Kiara Advani&#8217;s acting abilities and flexibility are taking her to great heights. It appears that acting has always run in her veins. She once shared in her cover interview with Vogue magazine that she was a full Hindi film buff in a school where it was &#8216;cool&#8217; to watch English films. Every time her friends contacted her, she would flip to an English channel. When no one was looking, she would listen to Govinda songs and deliver dialogues from Kabhi Khushi Kabhi Gham.\nShe first appeared in front of the camera at the very tender age of eight years while shooting an advertisement for baby cream along with her mother. Well, most famous for her breakout role as Priti in Kabir Singh, Kiara Advani is on an unstoppable roll of delivering one blockbuster after another. She made her debut in Fugly and has even acted in 2 Telugu movies. After spreading her roots in the soils of Bollywood, she even left a mark on the OTT platform with the movie \u2018Guilty\u2019 and gave a critically acclaimed performance in \u2018Lust Stories,\u2019 both of which were directed by Karan Johar. Apart from having a family which has strong connections with Bollywood big shots, she was also fortunate to be mentored by Salman Khan.\nThis stunning actress has fourteen million followers on Instagram alone, and all of them are always trying to catch a glimpse of her not so &#8216;humble&#8217; abode.\u00a0\nKiara Advani lives at the Planet Godrej building in Mahalaxmi, which is one of the area&#8217;s high-end developments. Planet Godrej&#8217;s apartments provide stunning 360-degree views of the Mahalaxmi Racecourse, the magnificent Haji Ali Mosque, and the much-loved Arabian Sea. The Mahalaxmi Race Course and the gorgeous Arabian Sea are seen from Advani&#8217;s property. Now, without any further ado, let&#8217;s quickly dive into this beautiful apartment. Have a Glance!\nLiving room with all-white aesthetics\u00a0\nStarting with the imperative part of the house, which is the living room. The living room gives out the first glimpse of the interiors of an abode, therefore it is indispensable to design this space magnificently, and it should be true to the owner&#8217;s personality. Kiara Advani&#8217;s plush living room is nothing less than perfection as it oozes her vibe and aesthetic sense. This area is lit up with natural sunlight with floor-to-wall ceiling windows, allowing fresh air to enter which helps in keeping the place buoyant. It provides a panoramic view of the Mahalaxmi race course and Mumbai\u2019s skyline. The whole theme of the room is white with a splash of gold. This is a great choice of colour because white creates an illusion of space and gives a bright aura to the room. The room is decorated with a huge white leather couch. She has added a white faux fur carpet to top off the whole decor, giving it a luxurious yet comfy feel. There is a huge potted plant next to the sofa, which adds a pop of colour. The couch is also laden with fancy plush pink and silver cushions. The wall directly above the sofa has a collection of mirrors which also helps in decluttering the space. Lastly, to bind all these elements together, the entire room is adorned with a textured gold wall. This whole decor is sure to give the guests an accurate impression of Kiara Advani\u2019s vibe and mirrors her unquestionable taste.\u00a0\nBalcony with a picturesque view\nThe living room opens up to a large spacious balcony with a breathtaking view of the Mumbai skyline as well as the Arabian Sea. This alone sets this balcony class apart, but to take it a step further, Kiara did not shy away from decorating her entire balcony in white theme too. The outdoor furniture in the balcony is made up of cane material that is ideal for the outdoors. On one side of the balcony, the entire wall is textured golden, which undoubtedly adds beauty. In addition, a textured brown wall, colourful artwork in red and black colours, and gold vases provide contrast and warmth to this nook. It is quite clear from her Instagram posts that she loves to enjoy a piping hot cup of tea with her near and dear ones at the balcony spot. It is a dream for many. The balcony spot appears to be idyllic to watch Mumbai\u2019s picturesque skyline.\nInstagram and Pinterest-worthy nook\nMoving on to another most pictured spot in the apartment which is tucked away in a corner of her living room. Kiara loves to take pictures of all her mesmerizing outfits and red-carpet looks in front of this Instagram and Pinterest-worthy backdrop. This spot is adorned with an overall theme of mirrors and glass. The wall is covered with mosaic style small mirrors, a side glass table decorated with roses in a silver vase and big candles that serves as a backdrop for photos taken before the red carpet.\nDine like a star\u00a0\nThere are many dazzling mirrors on the wall of the dining area. The modular spacious kitchen is striking and is well lit. It has white panelling all around which gives out a grandeur vibe. In addition, there are a lot of floral decorations to add colour and freshness.\nKiara and her love for flowers\u00a0\nKiara is fond of flowers, and her love for them is quite evident from the interiors of her abode. Flowers do bring the energy of an entire place to a high. However, Kiara\u2019s face is as beautiful as any fresh flower, and the vitality in her eyes is as dazzling as any fresh flower lighting someone&#8217;s day. Her fondness for flowery designs may be seen in the outfits she wears. Kiara looks stunning in floral designs, whether it&#8217;s a floral blouse, a floral dress, or a floral lehenga. Statement items like flowers are used to add a hint of colours and liveliness to one\u2019s life. The flower-power keeps the place looking fresh and fragrant at all times. Kiara&#8217;s home appears to be brimming with the beauty of flowers, whether in large pots or dazzling vases. The whole layout of the apartment is smartly planned and well-executed. The formal sitting area is separated from the bedrooms by a long, well-lit corridor. This ensures the privacy of the hostess when she throws a party at her luxe abode. The corridor is laden with a lot of family and friends pictures to add a personal touch. There are also some beautiful artworks in this corridor.\u00a0 With creamy wall paint and wood panelling on t