            "content_html": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We all know&nbsp;<strong>Chunky Pandey&nbsp;</strong>as a funny actor who is responsible for making us laugh hard through his exceptional acting skills.&nbsp;<strong>Chunky Pandey&nbsp;</strong>has made his mark in the film industry and has worked on many successful projects alongside big names. He lives in&nbsp;<strong>Mumbai&#8217;s Pali Hill&nbsp;</strong>area that is famously known for many&nbsp;<strong>celeb homes</strong>.&nbsp;<strong>Chunky&nbsp;</strong>lives with his wife&nbsp;<strong>Bhavana Pandey&nbsp;</strong>and their two beautiful daughters&nbsp;<strong>Ananya Pandey&nbsp;</strong>and Rysa Pandey.<em>&nbsp;</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chunky Pandey&#8217;s</strong>&nbsp;<strong>house&nbsp;</strong>is a perfect exemplar of a contemporary architectural design. He has given his bungalow a minimal but appealing approach. His star daughter&nbsp;<strong>Ananya Pandey&nbsp;</strong>has also shared some sneak peeks of their stylish abode from her well-known official Instagram handle. You will find some of her pics that she has taken inside their plush home when you scroll through her account. You can also Google&nbsp;<strong>Ananya Pandey house,&nbsp;</strong>and you&#8217;ll see some stunning photos of their abode.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Even though the&nbsp;<strong>Pali hill&nbsp;</strong>area is packed with countless notable&nbsp;<strong>celebrity homes</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Chunky Pandey</strong>&nbsp;<strong>house&nbsp;</strong>still manages to stand out due to an assortment of aspects, some of which we&#8217;re going to look at further in the blog.&nbsp;<strong>Chunky Pandey house</strong> is structured with many luxurious amenities like a home bar, garden and a vast lounge where the whole family gets together to spend some leisure time.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The house is built considering the wind directions to maximize the natural light and air ventilation throughout the structure. It also consists of an open to sky terrace, which the Pandey family often uses to rejuvenate themselves. The family additionally has pooches that live with them in one of the lush neighbourhoods of <strong>Mumbai</strong>. Ananya and Rysa are frequently seen in the living room and other areas with their pet canines. The living area is intended to look like a glasshouse, with mirrors adorning the walls. Chunky Pandey bought his opulent Pali Hill home in the 1990s when his career was at its pinnacle.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In front of the cottage are numerous varieties of plants. Ananya Pandey is frequently spotted doing yoga or simply painting at her favourite station around their home garden. She also relaxes on the terrace when she has a few minutes to spare. Now, let&#8217;s go over some interesting aspects of this property that make it worth the stare.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Key Facts about Chunky Pandey\u2019s Home D\u00e9cor</strong></h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Natural surrounding</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The bungalow is surrounded by natural greenery, which enhances the outward view of the house. Greenery surely helps in protecting the property from severe weathering effects. This idea also assists in safeguarding the health of the occupants as fresh air leads to healthy breathing and minimizes the chances of catching an infection.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Also, they&#8217;ve made a home garden inside, which contains diverse families of plants adding to the house&#8217;s charm. Plants are also said to be beneficial in reducing stress, which we can guess may be the reason for the Pandey family&#8217;s stress-free and attractive looks. You may have seen some Instagram pictures of <strong>Ananya Pandey&nbsp;</strong>in which she is seen roaming around their garden and clicking photos simultaneously. The modern architectural look in combination with the natural surrounding never fails to make the house look aesthetically alluring.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Correlative concept</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The house&#8217;s overall tone is very coordinated, and all parts of the building are interrelated in such a manner that adds to its beauty. All structural units like the living room, passages, bedrooms, etc., are laid out functionally to ease the accessibility aspect of the design.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">And the furniture used in different areas is also pretty rich looking and cohesive. For example, if we talk about the living room, Panday&#8217;s living room is full of fascinating details, despite its statement-making carpeting. The room has black and white baroque couches, velvety ebony and gold coffee table, and numerous enormous vases bursting with flowers, all in keeping with the space&#8217;s colour scheme. But wait, there&#8217;s more! The party area contains furniture that offers unexpected splashes of colour to the room, perfectly blending distinct aesthetics.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A handful of shiny yellow pots and a vintage-style side table in a cheery shade of bright blue adds a character to space. The small elements are what tie the entire area together. The elaborate gold carvings on the table, for example, coordinate with the print on the black and white couches. The cohesive approach helps in building a sophisticated image of the house without making it look contrasting.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Functional illumination</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a bustling city like Mumbai, it&#8217;s critical that one&#8217;s home feels like a hideaway with fresh air to breathe and sufficient sunlight- <strong>Ananya Pandey&#8217;s home</strong> covers all of these factors. The actress\u2019 apartment changes into a sun-drenched paradise throughout the day, thanks to the numerous floor-to-ceiling glass doors. Open spaces are created smartly to pass the light in every part of the house. The sunlight falling on the house during the daytime fetches the classy design of the home.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The doors also provide a view of the Panday&#8217;s outdoor area, which has rows and rows of plants, creating a relaxing atmosphere. Panday regularly visits the grassy spot to photograph her OOTDs before heading out to events, and she even celebrated Raksha Bandhan with her cousins there. The Panday&#8217;s also enjoy putting up their Christmas tree by the glass doors which helps in creating a pleasant festive cornucopia.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Good light and air ventilation help sustain the plant life surrounding the bungalow and their interior garden. In addition, all the windows and verandahs are smartly designed to amplify the brightness all over the house.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Pleasant interior d\u00e9cor</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">No matter how great any house looks from the outside, if it is not done correctly internally, it just doesn&#8217;t pass the vibe check.&nbsp; The interior of the house is very crucial in enriching the outlook of the home. So appropriate design measures are needed to be taken while doing the home d\u00e9cor to enhance the residence&#8217;s internal feels. And as we are talking about <strong>Chunky Pandey\u2019s house</strong>, it just fulfils every requirement of a perfect interior design.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The interior of the house is done quite well. A look inside the Panday family&#8217;s&nbsp;<strong>Mumbai&nbsp;</strong>house reveals that it is everything but simple. While Ananya Panday&#8217;s living space is predominantly black and white, new photographs show her posing for a party in a cosy area with rich, dark green walls. How does one go about matching colours like that? The room&#8217;s furnishings are filled with black and white pieces (note the ivory couch bed and monochrome artwork), allowing the room&#8217;s dramatic walls to take centre stage. A red animal figurine on the bedside table is one of the only other sources of colour in the room. A touch of synergy is added to the home&#8217;s loo with black and white tile identical to that in the hall.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">And coming to&nbsp;<strong>Ananya Pandey&#8217;s&nbsp;</strong>bedroom- gives us inspiration on how to be different from the typical yet sophisticated. The bedroom has been well decorated with oak flooring and crisp white walls. The entire bedroom has a basic feel to it. The living area features monochrome and patterned glossy flooring and vintage and nostalgic wooden interior d\u00e9cor motifs. The large glass windows are a major medium through which a lot of light enters, and the turquoise-hued table is embellished with gold. The rooms are decorated in sophisticated and elegant colours. Teal blue velvet chairs and couches are accented with olive green cushions. The spiral staircase leads to another peaceful spot in the house, designed to look like a loft. The overall interior essence of the house is precisely cultured which gives a contemporary vibe to the abode.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Celebration area</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This house is topped up with many luxurious amenities, one of which is their party space that is specially designed to celebrate family achievements. In Bollywood, entertainment is a major facet of life, and the Panday\u2019s home is well-equipped for throwing B-town hottest parties.&nbsp;<strong>Chunky Pandey&#8217;s</strong>&nbsp;bar, which is also one of&nbsp;<strong>Ananya Pandey&nbsp;</strong>and mom&nbsp;<strong>Bhavana Pandey&#8217;s</strong> favourite photo spot, has to be one of the most appealing nooks. The mirrored bar is encircled by velvety violet bar seats and has its pale blue cabinet stocked with bar necessities. Although the area&#8217;s colours are dark, the glass accents on the bar blend in magnificently with a spectrum of dazzling mirrors in the living room.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You may also have seen this party room in the stories posted by&nbsp;<strong>Ananya Pandey</strong>&nbsp;on Instagram<strong>, </strong>in which she is seen having fun with her friends. This area is perfect for times like lockdown when clubs and pubs in the city are shut, and there&#8217;s nowhere to go.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ending remarks</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chunky Pandey&nbsp;</strong>as an actor, has seen many ups and downs, and there was a time in his career when he had to introduce himself in the Bangladeshi film industry because of no projects in Bollywood. However, he bounced back with more energy and showed his worth to the world in the best way possible. He now owns this luxurious home in&nbsp;<strong>Mumbai&#8217;s&nbsp;</strong>suburb locality and lives with his family over there.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chunky purchased this house when he was doing well as an actor, and obviously, he&#8217;s done many changes to the property to keep its design relative to modern trends. His abode is among the top <strong>celebrity homes</strong>&nbsp;located in&nbsp;<strong>Mumbai&nbsp;</strong>that fans don&#8217;t miss out on looking. The actor also owns restaurants that he and his wife run together.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The bottom line is that the Pandey family home is worth a look when you are looking for&nbsp;<strong>celeb home&nbsp;</strong>inspiration to overhaul the architectural design of your house in a timeless fashion to keep the depiction relevant for years to come.</p>\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\n\n        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>Which other celeb homes are located in Pali hill?</h2>  