orning the walls. Chunky Pandey bought his opulent Pali Hill home in the 1990s when his career was at its pinnacle.\nIn front of the cottage are numerous varieties of plants. Ananya Pandey is frequently spotted doing yoga or simply painting at her favourite station around their home garden. She also relaxes on the terrace when she has a few minutes to spare. Now, let&#8217;s go over some interesting aspects of this property that make it worth the stare.\nKey Facts about Chunky Pandey\u2019s Home D\u00e9cor\nNatural surrounding\nThe bungalow is surrounded by natural greenery, which enhances the outward view of the house. Greenery surely helps in protecting the property from severe weathering effects. This idea also assists in safeguarding the health of the occupants as fresh air leads to healthy breathing and minimizes the chances of catching an infection.\nAlso, they&#8217;ve made a home garden inside, which contains diverse families of plants adding to the house&#8217;s charm. Plants are also said to be beneficial in reducing stress, which we can guess may be the reason for the Pandey family&#8217;s stress-free and attractive looks. You may have seen some Instagram pictures of Ananya Pandey&nbsp;in which she is seen roaming around their garden and clicking photos simultaneously. The modern architectural look in combination with the natural surrounding never fails to make the house look aesthetically alluring.\nCorrelative concept\nThe house&#8217;s overall tone is very coordinated, and all parts of the building are interrelated in such a manner that adds to its beauty. All structural units like the living room, passages, bedrooms, etc., are laid out functionally to ease the accessibility aspect of the design.\nAnd the furniture used in different areas is also pretty rich looking and cohesive. For example, if we talk about the living room, Panday&#8217;s living room is full of fascinating details, despite its statement-making carpeting. The room has black and white 